    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides an overview of the status of IPv6 deployment in 2022.  Specifically, it looks at the degree of adoption of IPv6 in the industry, analyzes the remaining challenges, and proposes further investigations in areas where the industry has not yet taken a clear and unified approach in the transition to IPv6.  It obsoletes RFC 6036.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
